name: SevenAteNine
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: seven eight nine
des:
Practice and perfect your grasp of basic math operations with Alexa! Whether you're learning to add for the first time or just want to keep sharp, this skill has it all and is suitable for people of all ages!

This skill covers the following four operations: addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. If you haven't yet grasped these operations yet, use this skill's practice mode to take time and gain mastery! Feeling confident about your mastery? Then use this skill's play mode to answer as many questions as you can in 60 seconds! The more you get right, the harder they become! And: you get bonus points for speed!

If you enjoyed this skill and want to check out some of my other skills, feel free to checkout my website here:

https://alexa-skill-dev.gitlab.io/alexaWebsite/

Enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
